<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Confirm Your Email - ActiveRabbit</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 16px 12px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }

    .content {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #667eea;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 8px 0 16px 0;
    }

    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .note {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" valign="middle">
          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin:0 auto;">
            <tr>
              <td valign="middle" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                <%= image_tag "faviicons/favicon-512.png",
                  width: 50,
                  height: 50,
                  alt: "ActiveRabbit",
                  title: "ActiveRabbit",
                  style: "display:block;"
                %>
              </td>

              <td valign="middle" style="text-align:left;">
                <div style="font-size:18px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.2; margin:0; color:#ffffff;">
                  ActiveRabbit
                </div>
                <div style="font-size:13px; line-height:1.2; margin-top:4px; opacity:0.9; color:#ffffff;">
                  AI-Powered Error Tracking
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h1>Confirm Your Email Address</h1>

    <p>Hi there!</p>

    <p>Thanks for creating an account on <strong>ActiveRabbit</strong> - AI-powered error tracking for Rails applications.</p>

    <p>Please confirm your email address (<strong><%= @email %></strong>) to get started with error monitoring.</p>

    <div class="button-wrapper">
      <a href="<%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>" class="button">Confirm Email Address</a>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      If you didn't create an account with ActiveRabbit, you can safely ignore this email.
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        ActiveRabbit - AI-Powered Error Tracking for Rails<br>
        <a href="https://activerabbit.ai">activerabbit.ai</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
